[According to the news release above, the total number of cases in
Hong Kong is now 494. We continue to await further information on the
extent of the outbreak in neighboring China. Updated information on
the epidemiology of the outbreak in the affected regions and the
characteristics of the strains of _Streptococcus pyogenes_ involved
would be useful and most appreciated.

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of Hong Kong and neighboring
China and Macau can be accessed at http://healthmap.org/r/0_xc. -
Mod.ML]
